node.text:
On Friday, 7/16 fly on over to #NintendoNYC and purchase the Zelda & Loftwing #amiibo. 

This amiibo features two characters on a single base and can be used to travel between the surface and the sky in The Legend of #Zelda: #SkywardSwordHD.

node.text:
On Friday, 7/16 stop by #NintendoNYC to purchase The Legend of #Zelda: #SkywardSword HD specially-designed Joy-Con controllers for $79.99! 

The right Joy-Con controller is themed after the Master Sword, while the left features a Hylian Shield motif.
